node.text:
Hey. Today is my bd and I have some gift for you guys!!! 
 
So Long story short  I made a filter !!! 😆❤️❤️❤️❤️😮‍💨💋 
I meant I didn’t make it of course 🙈 my good friend @davidxlyons put it together for me and I am just so obsessed 🤩❤️😭 tap to change colors, there’s green pink and the purple :) 

you can grab it from my page bitween igtv and tagged pictures, under the ✨ icon  or from my storys ❤️

Pls enjoy taking the cute pictures and videos I can’t wait to see you with it 😭❤️

Thank you so much for your love and support for 15 years of blowing glass.  really appreciate everyone joining my journey. It has been a great one ! I am 45 today and 20 years since I moved to USA 😆❤️ so grateful 💋 

Thank you so much from all the birthday wishes as well. I love you so much! 😘❤️ 

#filter #kiwi #sakibomb #davidlyons

This piece is already sold, 
Thank you so much for giving a great home @princesschiichii ❤️ I love your growing collections!! 💕 

Also thank you so much @areysocal for the beautiful photos ❤️
